      </div>

      <h1 class="title">
        <span class="title-main">CoderClaw</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="tagline" id="tagline">Self-hosted, developer-first multi‑agent coding workflows.</p>

      <p class="description">
        Transition from coding to managing business outcomes.<br/>
